org.wildfly.swarm.spi.api

Class Module

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wildfly.swarm.spi.api.Module

  • public class Module
extends Object
    JBoss Modules module descriptor.

    If a module is added to an archive, this descriptor is returned in order to allow specific customization regarding exports, services, etc.

    Author:
    Ken Finnigan
    See Also:
    JBossDeploymentStructureContainer.addModule(String), JBossDeploymentStructureContainer.addModule(String, String)
